{"tid":1982103,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"香港獨立之後應該要推舉sigma成為我地既哲人王(Philosopher king)","createTime":"2020-04-21T04:43:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-21T07:42:19.000Z","uid":66260,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ee0cb1ef13e13531cfb71f2597929b3fb48f7fef","tid":1982103,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T04:43:53.000Z","msg":"在〔理想國〕(Republic)一書中，柏拉圖(Plato, 427~347 B.C.)透過蘇格拉底(Socrates, 470~399 B.C.)與別人的對話來提倡一烏托邦式的教育系統，其最終目的在於培養哲學王，作為理想國的政策立法者和決策者。「政治權力與哲學因此放在同一人手中」，且大眾將極快地了解到由哲人王統治的優點。<br />\n<br />\n佢唔會攞刀斬你，只會用嚴密既邏輯令你無話可說<br />\n咁有學識既人應該要成為我地既統治階層"},{"pid":"7beb68b3dfe3daeb9423a52ae5f6a6efba157063","tid":1982103,"uid":75556,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T04:51:20.000Z","msg":"又做神"},{"pid":"3b72b60160c6f0416760e52d1f2f9ce4aed5f83c","tid":1982103,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7beb68b3dfe3daeb9423a52ae5f6a6efba157063","tid":1982103,"uid":75556,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T04:51:20.000Z","msg":"又做神"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T05:00:54.000Z","msg":"真心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aef30c21d5c5d171fcea0e00ea50a8a4d71e6643","tid":1982103,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7beb68b3dfe3daeb9423a52ae5f6a6efba157063","tid":1982103,"uid":75556,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T04:51:20.000Z","msg":"又做神"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T05:06:07.000Z","msg":"起底就覺得膠"},{"pid":"0ba1e729ed254269e968f5a4b4b29c4cb1ade543","tid":1982103,"uid":217108,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7beb68b3dfe3daeb9423a52ae5f6a6efba157063","tid":1982103,"uid":75556,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T04:51:20.000Z","msg":"又做神"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T05:07:36.000Z","msg":"明顯得罪大勢力 比人搞緊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e14e